full_text:
Week 6 #tidytuesday. 

I aimed to convey emotions rather than information. Below are the 1006 names of the TA. Names have been shaded so that they are not very visible, which reflects the fact that they faced great discrimination during WWII. 

#TuskegeeAirmenChallenge #RStats https://t.co/SCzg06t4zE
